channel.title: So how dead is scripting?
channel.description:
Ive been out of the cheating scene for around 5 years or so now.
So, i really dont know much about whats new, whats possible and whats current.
But how dead is scripting? Are we still able to completly macro our character to train the skills, handle all randoms, show enough of human interaction to prove its not a bot and rinse/repeat?
